                    "body": "Could I ask if there's a status update on this since May? I'd really like to use Textile in my app (preferably Markdown but I just need some sort of formatting).\r\n\r\nIf it helps here is a [great sample|http:\/\/www.textism.com\/tools\/textile\/?sample=2] you can use for testing.",
