                    },
                    "body": "27 oct the last update, changed from major to critical... if critical bugs take this long to fix, how long does it take to get major issues to be fixed?!\r\n\r\nPlease people, FIX THIS ASAP, this way the textile parser is realy not a viable option to use...",
