                    },
                    "body": "Besides the obvious bug this issue describes... there is more:\r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/textile.thresholdstate.com\/\r\n\r\nThis page allows you to see what is supposed to be possible using textile, but something basic as ==<html not to be parsed>== and notextile. are unknown to the parser ...\r\n\r\nThis renders it just about unusable... ",
